            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E8%80%81%E8%8A%B1%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E9%80%8F%E6%94%AF%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%E8%80%81%E8%8A%B1%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E6%98%AF%E7%9C%BC%E7%9D%9B%E9%80%8F%E6%94%AF%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#年轻人老花眼其实是眼睛透支了#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[苦涩]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/7e/2021_bitter_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%80%81%E8%8A%B1%E7%9C%BC%E5%92%8C%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%80%81%E8%8A%B1%E7%9C%BC%E5%92%8C%E9%95%BF%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E7%8E%A9%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%9C%89%E5%85%B3%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#老花眼和长时间玩手机有关吗#</span></a> 医生表示，老花眼实际上是肌肉调节力随着年纪下降了。“早老花”可以理解为特殊类型的视疲劳。因为用眼用得透支，导致肌肉调节功能不配合近距离用眼。医生告诫重度用眼爱好者，尽量减少近距离用眼。 <a href="http://t.cn/A6pJf5XF" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> ]]></description>
